description: The document.fonts API dynamically loads custom fonts and tracks when fonts are loading or ready to use.
description_html: The document.fonts API dynamically loads custom fonts and tracks when fonts are loading or ready to use.
name: Font loading

chrome.notes: Chrome does not expose the FontFaceSet interface directly, and is only available through Document.fonts or WorkerGlobalScope.fonts.
